comments: Nesmith (IND) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
White (BOS) swipes his hands down and initiates contact with Haliburton's (IND) arm that occurs prior to Haliburton's gather.
Hield (IND) is already in Brown's (BOS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
After the pick, White (BOS) and Turner (IND) briefly engage and quickly disengage and marginal contact occurs as they roll toward the basket.
Brown (BOS) jumps toward Haliburton (IND) and initiates contact with Haliburton's body that affects his follow-through.
Haliburton (IND) and Nesmith (IND) both avoid making contact with Holiday's (BOS) arm during their steal attempts at the end of the drive.
Haliburton (IND) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Holiday (BOS) cleanly deflects Haliburton's (IND) pass and the ball touches the baseline out of bounds. Possession is correctly retained by the Pacers.
Tatum (BOS) legally contests Hield's (IND) jump shot attempt.
Turner (IND) cleanly deflects the ball away from White (BOS) as he attempts to pass at the end of the drive.
Horford (BOS) contests Nesmith's (IND) shot near the rim, and the contact as he finishes at the rim is marginal.
White (BOS) and Haliburton (IND) both make clean contact with the ball during their pursuit for the rebound, and any follow-through contact is deemed incidental.
Holiday (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball as he defends Nesmith's (IND) pass attempt.
Holiday (BOS) is moving alongside Hield's (IND) path and Hield loses control of the ball on his own as he attempts to spin away.
Hield (IND) brings his forearm towards Tatum's (BOS) front and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Hield (IND) brings his arm into a vertical position and absorbs the marginal contact that occurs with Tatum (BOS) during the play at the basket.
White (BOS) commits a take foul on Nesmith (IND).
Brown (BOS) commits a take foul on Hield (IND).
Nesmith (IND) kicks the ball away from Tatum (BOS) on the perimeter.
Brown (BOS) commits a take foul on Brown (IND).
Hield (IND) brings his hands toward Tatum's (BOS) path and marginal contact occurs before he makes clean contact with the ball to deflect it away from Tatum.
Tatum (BOS) commits a take foul on Hield (IND).
Hield (IND) cleanly intercepts the inbound pass intended for Hauser (BOS).
